<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> <span class="c4">[٥]</span> وَتَسْبِيحُ رُكُوعٍ وَسُجُودٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٦]</span> وَقَوْلُ: <span class="c2">«رَبِّ اغْفِرْ لِي»</span> مَرَّةً مَرَّةً.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
