<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمَا عَدَا ذَلِكَ وَالشُّرُوطَ:</span> سُنَّةٌ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span class="c5"> فَالرُّكْنُ وَالشَّرْطُ:</span> لَا يَسْقُطَانِ سَهْواً وَجَهْلاً.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
